        <abstract>
            <p>Sends some trees to CD.</p> 
<p>Would be pleased to receive the copy of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> offered by CD as gift.</p> 
            <p>Will give CD any tree or shrub he may want.</p> 
<p>Refers to curious strawberry hybrids noticed in <hi rend="italic">Journal of Horticulture</hi> [I. Anderson-Henry, "Crossing strawberries", <hi rend="italic">J. Hortic.</hi> n.s. 4 (1863): 45–6].</p> 
